Control Flow Operations:
NOP
HALT

JMP-CON reg1 reg2
JMP-NCO reg1
CON = Conditional
NCO = No Conditional


ALU OPCODES:
ADD reg1 reg2 reg3
SUB reg1 reg2 reg3
MUL reg1 reg2 reg3
DIV reg1 reg2 reg3
AND reg1 reg2 reg3
OR reg1 reg2 reg3
XOR reg1 reg2 reg3
NOT reg1 reg2 reg3


REGISTERS OPCODES:
REG-SET reg1 value
REG-CP reg1 reg2


RAM OPCODES:
RAM-SET reg1 reg2
RAM-SET Addresses value

RAM-GET reg1 reg2
RAM-GET Direccion output-register


GPU OPCODES:
GPU-PRINT reg1 reg2
GPU-PRINT ASCII color-code
# the color code can be FF00FF (magenta) for example
